Context

Travelling in Iceland, I want to learn something from a numbers perspective as well. here, I am examining the data available for accommodation.

The Statistical Office of Icceland has a database that is accessible via an API that seems to come from the Swedish Statistical office, and handily enough has an R package as well :-)
